    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 将斥资数百万美元游说纽约放宽租赁禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/airbnb-to-spend-millions-in-lobbying-new-york-to-ease-rental-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb 公司正向纽约的两项政治活动投入数百万美元，以抵制短期租赁限制措施。该限制措施导致该公司在纽约一年内 80% 以上的房源下线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/airbnb-to-spend-millions-in-lobbying-new-york-to-ease-rental-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的 Poilievre 承诺扭转资本利得税改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/canada-s-poilievre-promises-to-reverse-capital-gains-tax-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 承诺，如果当选，将取消资本利得税纳入税率的上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/canada-s-poilievre-promises-to-reverse-capital-gains-tax-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:37:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队准备对俄罗斯和伊朗实施石油制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-team-readies-oil-sanctions-plan-for-russia-deal-iran-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的顾问正在制定一项广泛的制裁策略，以促进未来几个月俄罗斯与乌克兰达成外交协议，同时对伊朗和委内瑞拉施压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-team-readies-oil-sanctions-plan-for-russia-deal-iran-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚在社交媒体上加强竞选规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/romania-toughens-campaign-rules-for-social-media-after-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在被取消的总统选举重新举行之前，罗马尼亚批准了针对 TikTok 和 Facebook 等社交媒体平台的更严格的竞选规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/romania-toughens-campaign-rules-for-social-media-after-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:44:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国将限制对企业的征税，重点关注对富人的征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/french-government-to-limit-levy-on-firms-focus-on-taxing-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预算部长阿梅莉·德蒙查兰表示，法国新政府计划将对企业的临时征税期限限制为一年，并将重点向富人征税，以寻求缩小赤字的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/french-government-to-limit-levy-on-firms-focus-on-taxing-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普连任前美国敲定向 Rivian 和 Plug Power 投资数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，拜登政府准备在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普返回白宫之前，为电动汽车制造商 Rivian Automotive Inc. 和氢能公司 Plug Power Inc. 完成数十亿美元的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 02:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油资源丰富的加蓬选择哈佛毕业生帮助解决债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-rich-gabon-picks-new-economy-minister-to-tackle-debt-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加蓬军事领导人布里斯·奥利吉·恩圭马选择了一位新经济部长来解决这个中非石油生产国的债务问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-rich-gabon-picks-new-economy-minister-to-tackle-debt-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 19:22:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默对乌克兰的谨慎态度可能会在特朗普上台前失去影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-caution-on-ukraine-risks-loss-of-clout-ahead-of-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自俄罗斯全面入侵以来，英国就以大力支持乌克兰而闻名。但在首相基尔·斯塔默的任期内，泽连斯基总统的政府及其支持者对英国更为谨慎的做法越来越感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-caution-on-ukraine-risks-loss-of-clout-ahead-of-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 18:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默为任命前银行说客担任市政府职务辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-defends-naming-ex-banks-lobbyist-to-city-of-london-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默办公室表示，首相在去年任命了一位前金融业说客来监管她所代表的公司，但目前她仍致力于结束政府与企业之间的旋转门关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-defends-naming-ex-banks-lobbyist-to-city-of-london-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 17:44:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
